<inglise> I. (a) Support for economic transition and the establishment of a Euro-Mediterranean free-trade area shall include in particular: </inglise>
<eesti> I. a) Majandusliku &uuml;lemineku ja Euroopa-Vahemere vabakaubanduspiirkonna rajamise toetamine h&otilde;lmab eelk&otilde;ige: </eesti>
<inglise> - job creation and private sector development, including improvement of the business environment and support for SMEs, </inglise>
