<inglise> - upgrading of economic infrastructure, possibly to include the financial and taxation systems. </inglise>
<eesti> - majanduslike infrastruktuuride parandamist, sealhulgas v&otilde;imaluse korral ka finants- ja maksus&uuml;steemid. </eesti>
<inglise> (b) Operations in support of structural adjustment programmes, implemented on the basis of the following principles: </inglise>
<eesti> b) Struktuurilise kohandamise programmide toetusmeetmeid rakendatakse j&auml;rgmiste p&otilde;him&otilde;tete alusel: </eesti>
<inglise> - the support programmes shall be designed to restore the major financial balances and create an economic environment favourable to accelerated growth, while at the same time improving the well-being of the population, </inglise>
<eesti> - toetusprogrammide koostamise eesm&auml;rgiks on taastada finantstasakaal ja luua kiirenevat kasvu soodustav majanduskeskkond, parandades samal ajal elanikkonna heaolu, </eesti>
<inglise> - the support programmes shall be adapted to the particular situation of each country and take account of economic and social conditions, </inglise>
<eesti> - toetusprogramme kohandatakse vastavalt iga riigi olukorrale ning neis v&otilde;etakse arvesse majanduslikke ja sotsiaalseid tingimusi, </eesti>
<inglise> - the support programmes shall lay down measures intended, in particular, to alleviate the negative effects which the process of structural adjustment may have on social conditions and employment, especially for underprivileged sections of the population; </inglise>
<eesti> - toetusprogrammides n&auml;hakse ette kavandatavad meetmed, eelk&otilde;ige selleks, et leevendada struktuuriliste kohanduste v&otilde;imalikku negatiivset m&otilde;ju sotsiaalsetele tingimustele ja t&ouml;&ouml;h&otilde;ivele eriti elanikkonna sotsiaalselt t&otilde;rjutud osas, </eesti>
<inglise> - the support programmes shall be orientated towards the creation of a free-trade area with the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> - toetusprogrammid koostatakse eesm&auml;rgiga luua vabakaubanduspiirkond Euroopa &Uuml;hendusega, </eesti>
<inglise> - rapid disbursement shall be one of the main features of the support programmes. </inglise>
